<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-40-0066 </DOCNO><TEXT>This paper describes the working principles of a slip clutch which isused in a new model of flameproof winder for speed control. The designand the calculations of mechanical principles are presented. Applicationof such winder in mine shafts improves safety, reliability and productivity,and plays an active role in promoting automation of mine production.4 figs.</TEXT></DOC>